{"tid":2314874,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【電話騙案】一女子自稱係特務，企圖騙300萬","createTime":"2020-12-06T23:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T03:03:51.000Z","uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b524309d2bb7d931837136ecbe6f8b19d3de9f","tid":2314874,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T23:15:08.000Z","msg":"電騙案拘46人 當中30人稱自己是受害人 需做特務脫罪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201207/mobile/bkn-20201207000208141-1207_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201207%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201207000208141-1207_00822_001.html&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2jDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=cf6612f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201207/mobile/bkn-20201207000208141-1207_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n電話騙案急升，警方留意到騙徒近期經常稱自己是「特務」。東九龍總區重案組總督察莫子威表示，警方就電騙案拘捕的46人中，便有30人聲稱自己是「特務」，指自己亦是電騙案的受害人，被騙徒指違反某些法例，需要做特務洗脫罪名，如押送特定人士到銀行或是運送金錢等。莫強調，「特務唔係理由」，而特務在案件的參與程度已構成犯罪，呼籲市民若收到相關電話切勿相信，若有疑問，可致電警方防騙熱線「18222」救助。<br />\n莫子威表示，今年電騙案年齡最細的受害人只有14歲，他便是將騙款交到騙徒指派的「女特務」手上。該男童今年8月收到騙徒的電話，以為自己捲入內地的洗黑錢案中，並聽從騙徒的指示，數日後把家中所有的20萬港元現金全數親手交予一名「女特務」手上，其後他再被指派向父母索要現金，始令事件曝光，警方事後拘捕一名18歲「女特務」，她共涉4宗案件。<br />\n警方商業罪案調查科反詐騙協調中心總督察顏凱欣表示，今年的電話騙案中騙徒經常使用一個名為「安全防衛」的木馬程式，騙徒會透過傳送網站連結，讓受害人下載以進行「資產審查」，受害人下載後惡意木馬程式便會有不同銀行選項，令受害人輸入其網上銀行帳戶的資料及密碼，該程式更可刪除受害人手機的短訊內容，轉寄短訊到騙徒的手機，以截取受害人的一次性轉帳密碼，並在無形間轉走戶口的金錢。"},{"pid":"c3e801fb63d8a2985d420a152f31c2d0a31e67f4","tid":2314874,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T23:15:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201207/photo/bkn-20201207000208141-1207_00822_001_01p.jpg?20201207001101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201207000208141-1207_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20201207001101&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2jDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=df169e50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201207/photo/bkn-20201207000208141-1207_00822_001_01p.jpg?20201207001101</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201207/photo/bkn-20201207000208141-1207_00822_001_01p.jpg?20201207001101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201207000208141-1207_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20201207001101&h=007bb9c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5e242833eaceca75d628ee9bcf02e3faa7da492","tid":2314874,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用支為呀啦"},{"pid":"2f116949e391253a393a6391113a964a15f5ed59","tid":2314874,"uid":73915,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:56:18.000Z","msg":"特務警察未聽過？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2020/01/03/9159/wttp048p01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2020%2F01%2F03%2F9159%2Fwttp048p01a.jpg&h=2c5cb3fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fab5440dd913e6411c5ed136b37e4698eedd9a9f","tid":2314874,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:05:53.000Z","msg":"最鐘意話自稱拜登話完事之後會比個國務卿你做"},{"pid":"643386d1c0e9bff325a19b430388b0c15cce9c3f","tid":2314874,"uid":288505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:08:57.000Z","msg":"真係特務會同你講係特務咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做特務最緊要唔係隱藏身份，咁做同自爆有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4589feb17a01b0f32d902fc8fe818090240d969","tid":2314874,"uid":168730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:11:02.000Z","msg":"18歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17b6f84c584b3cadd2a9fa3e64f139aa6824277","tid":2314874,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":